    ... when != \(f1(...,x,...)\|<+...x...+>=E4\)
        when != \(while(...) S1\|for(...;...;...) S1\)
-   memset((T2)x,0,E1 * E0);
    ...
  } else S2
|
- memset((T2)x,0,E1 * E0);
